text.section:
Except as provided in subsection (b) of this section, an owner of an affected property shall give to the tenant of the affected property a notice, prepared by the Department, of the tenant's rights under §§ 6-817 and 6-819 of this subtitle, according to the following schedule:
At least 25% of the owner's affected properties by May 25, 1996;
At least 50% of the owner's affected properties by August 25, 1996;
At least 75% of the owner's affected properties by November 25, 1996; and
100% of the owner's affected properties by February 25, 1997.
